# tstack CLI

**Location:** `cli/` — Rust CLI for `tstack doctor`, `tstack add`, etc.

## Build & Run

```bash
cd cli && cargo build
cargo install --path .   # puts `tstack` on PATH
```

## Structure

| Path | Purpose |
|------|---------|
| `cli/src/main.rs` | Entry point |
| `cli/src/commands/` | Subcommands (add, doctor, list, run, status) |
| `cli/Cargo.toml` | Dependencies |

## Adding a Command

1. Add module in `cli/src/commands/mod.rs`
2. Implement in `cli/src/commands/<name>.rs`
3. Register in `main.rs` or mod
